Description: Functions for fitting longitudinal functional partial least
    squares regression models for longitudinal scalar-on-function data.
    The package includes tools for simulation-based data generation,
    pilot decomposition of longitudinal functional predictors into
    subject-specific functional intercept, subject-specific functional
    slope, and visit-specific deviation components, residualized
    supervised partial least squares construction, REML-based mixed-model
    fitting, coefficient-function reconstruction, smoothing, and BIC-based
    tuning of LFPLS components.
